<subSubSection pageId="122" pageNumber="880" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="122.[1451,2658,707,1564]" pageId="122" pageNumber="880">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1453,1798,1373,1406]" pageId="122" pageNumber="880">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCNRed List. Main threat to the Hairy-tailed Bat is intensive habitat destruction in south-eastern region of 
<collectingRegion country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="122" pageNumber="880">Sao Paulo State</collectingRegion>
. Both specimens were collected in protected areas.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
